Source: libdvdnav
Section: devel
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Philipp Hahn <pmhahn@titan.lahn.de>
Standards-Version: 3.5.6
Build-Depends: debhelper (>> 3.0.0), libdvdread2-dev

Package: libdvdnav-dev
Section: devel
Architecture: any
Depends: libdvdnav1 (= ${Source-Version}), libdvdread2-dev
Description: The DVD navigation library, development package
 This is the DVD navigation library, which provides an interface
 to the advanced features of DVDs, like menues, navigation, etc.
 .
 This package contains the header files and static library needed to
 compile applications that use libdvdnav1.

Package: libdvdnav1
Section: libs
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: The DVD navigation library
 This is the DVD navigation library, which provides an interface
 to the advanced features of DVDs, like menues, navigation, etc.
 .
 This package contains the libdvdnav1 runtime library.
